<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>随想 on Half Bit</title><link>https://run.halfbit.top/categories/%E9%9A%8F%E6%83%B3/</link><description>Recent content in 随想 on Half Bit</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 02 Sep 2022 02:20:44 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://run.halfbit.top/categories/%E9%9A%8F%E6%83%B3/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>谈谈工作</title><link>https://run.halfbit.top/post/work-vs-job/</link><pubDate>Fri, 02 Sep 2022 02:20:44 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://run.halfbit.top/post/work-vs-job/</guid><description>度过了这个苦夏，秋意习习，心情也豁然开怀，终于有心情一叙。 今天先聊聊工作。 不管再怎么不想聊，工作依然是最近几个月生活的绝对重心，遑论近几个月</description></item><item><title>核心逻辑？</title><link>https://run.halfbit.top/post/awareness/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 May 2022 21:38:37 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://run.halfbit.top/post/awareness/</guid><description>看到近期的互联网频发的裁员的消息，看到圈内非常多的讨论，身边各种人的现状，自己也经历去年并不很“划算”的一波跳槽，汇总了一大些“浴中奇思”，</description></item><item><title>0321 消极性的缺失</title><link>https://run.halfbit.top/post/0321-%E6%B6%88%E6%9E%81%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 21 Mar 2022 02:05:37 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://run.halfbit.top/post/0321-%E6%B6%88%E6%9E%81%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1/</guid><description>去年写过一篇文章《无聊时间》，是受到一期播客节目的启发。无独有偶，昨天又听到一期播客，又聊到类似的话题，从而读了主播推荐的韩炳哲的《倦怠社会</description></item><item><title>0315 心力</title><link>https://run.halfbit.top/post/0315-%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%9B/</link><pubDate>Wed, 16 Mar 2022 00:07:37 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://run.halfbit.top/post/0315-%E5%BF%83%E5%8A%9B/</guid><description>穆阿迪布之所以能做到英勇无畏，也许是因为他从一开始就知道结局，一步也不离开他预见到的路径。这一点，他说得非常清楚。“我的行为就是验证我的预言</description></item><item><title>0103 变、30 / 8</title><link>https://run.halfbit.top/post/0103-%E5%8F%9830-8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jan 2022 03:52:37 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://run.halfbit.top/post/0103-%E5%8F%983